myMemoryMIB.name: myMemoryMIB

revisions.description: Initial version of this MIB module.

myMemoryMIB.description: This module defines my system mibs.

Percent.name: Percent
Percent.description: An integer that is in the range of a percent value.

myMemoryPoolUtilizationTable.name: myMemoryPoolUtilizationTable
myMemoryPoolUtilizationTable.description: A table of memory pool utilization entries. Each of the objects provides a general idea of how much of the memory pool has been used over a given period of time.

myMemoryPoolUtilizationEntry.name: myMemoryPoolUtilizationEntry
myMemoryPoolUtilizationEntry.description: An entry in the memory pool utilization table.

myMemoryPoolIndex.name: myMemoryPoolIndex
myMemoryPoolIndex.description: An index that uniquely represents a Memory Pool.

myMemoryPoolName.name: myMemoryPoolName
myMemoryPoolName.description: A textual name assigned to the memory pool. This object is suitable for output to a human operator

myMemoryPoolCurrentUtilization.name: myMemoryPoolCurrentUtilization
myMemoryPoolCurrentUtilization.description: This is the memory pool utilization currently.

myMemoryPoolLowestUtilization.name: myMemoryPoolLowestUtilization
myMemoryPoolLowestUtilization.description: This is the memory pool utilization when memory used least.

myMemoryPoolLargestUtilization.name: myMemoryPoolLargestUtilization
myMemoryPoolLargestUtilization.description: This is the memory pool utilization when memory used most.

myMemoryPoolSize.name: myMemoryPoolSize
myMemoryPoolSize.description: This is the size of physical memory .

myMemoryPoolUsed.name: myMemoryPoolUsed
myMemoryPoolUsed.description: This is the memory size that has been used.

myMemoryPoolFree.name: myMemoryPoolFree
myMemoryPoolFree.description: This is the memory size that is free.

myMemoryPoolWarning.name: myMemoryPoolWarning
myMemoryPoolWarning.description: The first warning of memory pool.

myMemoryPoolCritical.name: myMemoryPoolCritical
myMemoryPoolCritical.description: The second warning of memory pool.

myNodeMemoryPoolTable.name: myNodeMemoryPoolTable
myNodeMemoryPoolTable.description: A table of node's memory pool utilization entries. Each of the objects provides a general idea of how much of the memory pool has been used over a given period of time.

myNodeMemoryPoolEntry.name: myNodeMemoryPoolEntry
myNodeMemoryPoolEntry.description: An entry in the node's memory pool utilization table.

myNodeMemoryPoolIndex.name: myNodeMemoryPoolIndex
myNodeMemoryPoolIndex.description: An index that uniquely represents a node's Memory Pool.

myNodeMemoryPoolName.name: myNodeMemoryPoolName
myNodeMemoryPoolName.description: A textual name assigned to the node's memory pool. This object is suitable for output to a human operator

myNodeMemoryPoolCurrentUtilization.name: myNodeMemoryPoolCurrentUtilization
myNodeMemoryPoolCurrentUtilization.description: This is the node's memory pool utilization currently.

myNodeMemoryPoolLowestUtilization.name: myNodeMemoryPoolLowestUtilization
myNodeMemoryPoolLowestUtilization.description: This is the node's memory pool utilization when memory used least.

myNodeMemoryPoolLargestUtilization.name: myNodeMemoryPoolLargestUtilization
myNodeMemoryPoolLargestUtilization.description: This is the node's memory pool utilization when memory used most.

myNodeMemoryPoolSize.name: myNodeMemoryPoolSize
myNodeMemoryPoolSize.description: This is the size of the node's physical memory .

myNodeMemoryPoolUsed.name: myNodeMemoryPoolUsed
myNodeMemoryPoolUsed.description: This is the node's memory size that has been used.

myNodeMemoryPoolFree.name: myNodeMemoryPoolFree
myNodeMemoryPoolFree.description: This is the node's memory size that is free.

myNodeMemoryPoolWarning.name: myNodeMemoryPoolWarning
myNodeMemoryPoolWarning.description: This is the first warning of the node's memory.

myNodeMemoryPoolCritical.name: myNodeMemoryPoolCritical
myNodeMemoryPoolCritical.description: This is the second warning of the node's memory.

myMemoryMIBCompliance.description: The compliance statement for entities which implement the My Memory MIB

myMemoryPoolUtilizationMIBGroup.description: A collection of objects providing memory pool utilization to a My agent.
